## Acceptance Criteria Check

From BA requirements:

- ✅ **API errors trigger an error modal instead of a toast notification** - Verified in axiosClient.ts, handleErrorModal called for non-400/401 errors
- ✅ **Error modal displays a user-friendly message without technical details** - Message extraction logic uses fallback, no stack traces or technical details shown
- ✅ **Error modal has a visible "Close" or "OK" button** - Close button present with proper styling and accessibility
