- ✅ **Only one error modal is visible at any time** - modalService.open replaces existing modal by design (verified in modalService implementation)
- ✅ **New API errors replace the currently displayed error modal** - Each call to handleErrorModal opens ERROR modal, which replaces previous
- ✅ **All existing API error toasts have been replaced with the modal** - notificationService.addErrorAlert deprecated, axiosClient uses handleErrorModal
- ✅ **The modal blocks interaction with underlying content until dismissed** - Modal component has overlay that blocks clicks (verified in Modal.tsx)

